	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div xml:id="div1" corresp="regest1">
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la">Salus et pax Christi.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la">Adhuc quiescunt omnia, nec scitur, quid concessurus sit <persName ref="p18538">cęsar</persName><note xml:id="fn1" type="footnote" n="1"><persName ref="p18538">Kaiser Karl V.</persName> schob eine Stellungnahme zum <placeName ref="l157">Frankfurter</placeName> Anstand hinaus; vgl. <bibl>Fuchtel</bibl> 196-200.</note>.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la">Quidam optare videntur <placeName ref="l361">Nurenbergensem</placeName> conventum<note xml:id="fn2" type="footnote" n="2">Zum geplanten Religionsgespräch in <placeName ref="l361">Nürnberg</placeName> s. oben <ref target="file11304">Nr. 1261</ref>, Anm. 6.</note> freti bona spe capi posse quosdam isto colloquio.</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la">Quod ut fiat, nos quoque optamus nichil tamen minus credentes; negamus enim rhete evangelicum<note xml:id="fn3" type="footnote" n="3">In Anspielung auf Bibelstellen wie <cit type="bible"><ref>Mt 4, 18f</ref></cit>; vgl. etwa <bibl>WA</bibl> IV 633, 5-16.</note> esse illas scandalis plenas concordantias<note xml:id="fna" type="footnote" n="a"><hi>korrigiert aus</hi> concordantiis.</note>, quando scilicet non fidei reddenda ratio, sed discutiendu[m]<pb type="edition" next="149"/><note xml:id="fnb" type="footnote" n="b"><hi>Randtext im Einband verdeckt.</hi></note>, quibus rationibus cum furibus et latronibus ineas amicitiam.</s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la">Interim de nobis vix sumus tam solliciti quam de vobis vestrisque ecclesiis; veremur enim, ne vestrum aliquot ad hoc quoque negotium rapiantur vel alliciantur.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la">Hoc vero si communibus votis fieret, minus esset periculi; sed si cum nova scissio[ne]<note xml:id="fnc" type="footnote" n="c"><hi>Randtext im Einband verdeckt.</hi></note> fiat, timendum est, ne ex uno malo nascant[ur]<note xml:id="fnd" type="footnote" n="d"><hi>Randtext im Einband verdeckt.</hi></note> multa, quod dominus avertat.</s>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la">Proxim[o]<note xml:id="fne" type="footnote" n="e"><hi>Randtext im Einband verdeckt.</hi></note> tabellione addam alia forte; hęrent enim adhuc omnia.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" ana="farewell">Interim vale, amantissime in domino, nosque semper ama.</s>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" ana="salute"><persName ref="p4082">Cuͦnradus</persName><note xml:id="fn4" type="footnote" n="4"><persName ref="p4082">Konrad Zwick</persName>.</note> frater et symmystę omnes salutant te studiosissime.</s>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la">Uxorem<note xml:id="fn5" type="footnote" ana="bio" n="5"><persName ref="p8051">Anna, geb. Adlischwyler</persName>.</note> tuam, matrem<note xml:id="fn6" type="footnote" ana="bio" n="6"><persName ref="p7042">Anna, geb. Wiederkehr</persName>.</note> et puellas<note xml:id="fn7" type="footnote" n="7">Gemeint sind <persName ref="p495">Bullingers</persName> Töchter <persName ref="p7224">Anna</persName>, <persName ref="p5608">Margaretha</persName> und <persName ref="p6609">Elisabeth</persName>.</note> omniaque tua<note xml:id="fnf" type="footnote" n="f">omniaque tua <hi>am Rande nachgetragen.</hi></note> salva iubeo.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la">Ex <placeName ref="l257">Constantia</placeName>, 24. maii 1539.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la">Tuus <persName ref="p4079">Io. Zvick</persName>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="la"><persName ref="p7201">Iacobum</persName><note xml:id="fn8" type="footnote" n="8"><persName ref="p7201">Jakob Zorn</persName>; vgl. oben <ref target="file11290">Nr. 1247</ref>.</note> illum, qui ex <placeName ref="l774">Turgoya</placeName> iniuste pulsus nunc apud vos est, commendo tibi; nam vere bonus est et magnam iniuriam pertulit<note xml:id="fng" type="footnote" n="g"><hi>vor</hi> pertulit <hi>ein gestrichener Buchstabe.</hi></note>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<note type="address">[Adresse auf der Rückseite:]</note>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="la">Domino <persName ref="p495">Hainricho Bullingero</persName>, <placeName ref="l587">Tigurino</placeName> episcopo insigniter pio, fratri meo charissimo.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
